g><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 28, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lul1714478408811.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lul1714478408811.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lul1714478408811.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"wij1665703009458\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $rscan\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"wij1665703009458___rscan_285792\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Find a substring within a string, starting from the end of the string.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"wij1665703009458__topic_d88562e1_d88563e1_d88564e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wij1665703009458__p_d88565e1_d88566e1_d88567e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$rscan</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Source</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">SearchFor</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"wij1665703009458__section_w4129ab1b7b5_w4130ab1b7_w4131ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wij1665703009458__p_d88568e1_d88569e1_d88570e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">vOutput = $rscan (\"The quick brown fox\", \"quick\")</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wij1665703009458__topic_d58977e1_d58978e1_d58979e1_d58980e1_d58981e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d188606e91\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"wij1665703009458__table_d9536e1_d9537e1_d9538e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wij1665703009458__table_d9536e1_d9537e1_d9538e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wij1665703009458__table_d9536e1_d9537e1_d9538e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wij1665703009458__table_d9536e1_d9537e1_d9538e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wij1665703009458__table_d9536e1_d9537e1_d9538e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Source</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wij1665703009458__table_d9536e1_d9537e1_d9538e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wij1665703009458__table_d9536e1_d9537e1_d9538e1__entry__3\">\n String in which the substring needs to be found.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wij1665703009458__table_d9536e1_d9537e1_d9538e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">SearchFor</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wij1665703009458__table_d9536e1_d9537e1_d9538e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wij1665703009458__table_d9536e1_d9537e1_d9538e1__entry__3\"> Substring to search for.\n                           <var class=\"keyword varname\">SearchFor</var> can be a constant string, regex string, or\n                        syntax string. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wij1665703009458__topic_d58982e1_d58983e1_d58984e1_d58985e1_d58986e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d188606e163\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wij1665703009458__p_d88577e1_d88578e1_d88579e1\">Position of the substring within the string.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wij1665703009458__topic_d58987e1_d58988e1_d58989e1_d58990e1_d58991e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d188606e173\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wij1665703009458__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wij1665703009458__topic_d58992e1_d58993e1_d58994e1_d58995e1_d58996e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d188606e182\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wij1665703009458__p_d88589e1_d88590e1_d88591e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$rscan</span> function looks for a string or a pattern in a string starting from the end of the string.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wij1665703009458__section_udy_yyg_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d188606e194\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$rscan</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example finds the first occurrence of literal\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">o</code> in the source string, when scanning from right to left.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"wij1665703009458__pre_ohl_zyg_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vOutput = $rscan(\"look for o\", \"o\")\n; vOutput = 10</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example finds the literal string <code class=\"ph codeph\">quick</code>\n               in the source string.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"wij1665703009458__pre_phl_zyg_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">OUTPUT = $rscan (\"The quick brown fox\", \"quick\")\n; OUTPUT = 5</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example finds a number (using the syntax string\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">\"#\"</code>) in the source string. It returns the position of first\n               number it encounters when scanning from right to left.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"wij1665703009458__pre_qhl_zyg_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vOutput = $rscan (\"The 1st quick brown fox came 2nd.\", $syntax(\"#\"))\n; OUTPUT = 30</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example finds the first occurrence of regex <code class=\"ph codeph\">o</code> in the\n               source string, when scanning from right to left.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104lul1714478408811_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"wij1665703009458__codeblock_u4m_2zd_gbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vOutput = $rscan(\"look for o\",$regex(\"o\"))\n; vOutput = 10</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example finds the first occurrence of regex <code class=\"ph codeph\">o</code> in the\n               source string with case-insensitive, when scanning from right to left.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104lul1714478408811_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"wij1665703009458__codeblock_j33_hzd_gbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vOutput = $rscan(\"look for O\",$regex(\"o\",\"i\"))\n; vOutput = 10</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mdy1714482565238.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$scan</a><p>Returns the position of a substring within a string.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_6812567\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_6812567\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$rscan Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 28, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $rscan Find a substring within a string, starting from the end of the string. $rscan ( Source , SearchFor ) Example: vOutput = $rscan (\"The quick brown fox\", \"quick\") Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Source String String in which the substring needs to be found. SearchFor String Substring to search for. SearchFor can be a constant string, regex string, or syntax string. Return Values Position of the substring within the string. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The $rscan function looks for a string or a pattern in a string starting from the end of the string. Example: Using $rscan The following example finds the first occurrence of literal o in the source string, when scanning from right to left. vOutput = $rscan(\"look for o\", \"o\") ; vOutput = 10 Copy The following example finds the literal string quick in the source string. OUTPUT = $rscan (\"The quick brown fox\", \"quick\") ; OUTPUT = 5 Copy The following example finds a number (using the syntax string \"#\" ) in the source string. It returns the position of first number it encounters when scanning from right to left. vOutput = $rscan (\"The 1st quick brown fox came 2nd.\", $syntax(\"#\")) ; OUTPUT = 30 Copy The following example finds the first occurrence of regex o in the source string, when scanning from right to left. Explain this code vOutput = $rscan(\"look for o\",$regex(\"o\")) ; vOutput = 10 Copy The following example finds the first occurrence of regex o in the source string with case-insensitive, when scanning from right to left. Explain this code vOutput = $rscan(\"look for O\",$regex(\"o\",\"i\")) ; vOutput = 10 Copy Related Links $scan Returns the position of a substring within a string. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}